description: This spatial coverage includes vector points and point labels that describe CORDIO and PRAREV in-water survey sites of the broader Djibouti Seascape. Each site has a set of fish and benthic community variables  distinguishing it from the surrounding sites. These characteristics include site name, functional group, mean  fish biomass (kg/ha) andmeanl fish abundance (individuals/ha).
name: Djibouti 2014 and  2016 Mean Corallivores Abundance (#/ha)
